com.worldpay.library.webservices.services.customers

Class CustomerResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.worldpay.library.webservices.services.BaseService
      • com.worldpay.library.webservices.services.ServiceResponse
        • com.worldpay.library.webservices.services.customers.CustomerResponse

  • public class CustomerResponse
extends ServiceResponse
    Contains customer information previously stored on the Gateway.

    The following values will be present in ALL Customer Responses:

    • getFirstName()
    • getLastName()
    • getAddress()
    • getEmail()
    • getPhone()

    The following values are optional in ALL Customer Responses:

    • getEmail()
    • isSendEmailReceipts()
    • getPhone()
    • getCompany()
    • getNotes()
    • getUserDefinedFields()
    • getPrimaryPaymentMethodId()
    • getPaymentMethods()
